样 的 方式 把 这样 的 错误 改回来 。
　
抗议 方法 ：
　
一 、 点击 http : / / www . google . com / support / maps / bin / request . py 后选 Suggestion
　
二 、 填上 你 的 电子邮件 地址 ， SUBJECT 写 上 Object   for   removing   Province   from   Taiwa
n
　
三 、 拷贝 下面 内容 （ 或 自己 认为 更 合适 的 表述 ） 到 MESSAGE ， 然后 按 SUBMIT
　
Dear   Google ,
　
In   your   map   listings ,   I   noticed   that   you   mistakenly   removed   " Province   of   Chi
na "   from   the   list   of   Taiwan ,   maybe   because   of   some   people \ ' s   weird   mail - sugge
stion ,   on   Sep   27   2005 .   It   is   not   a   good   change .   Please   fix   the   display   as   th
e   reasonable   format .
　
Taiwan   is   NOT   an   independent   nation .   More   than   161   countries   in   United   Natio
nals   claim   that   Taiwan   is   an   integral   part   of   China .   Something   such   as   curre
ncy ,   election ,   and   funny   government   cannot   uxtapose   a   province   with   its   moth
er   country .   Whether   some   minority   satisfy   or   not ,   a   province   of   a   country   is
much   more   appropriate   than   a   nation   by   definition .
　
Although   we   all   know   Taiwan   is   a   complex   problem ,   anyway ,   we   are   a   whole   fam
ily .   Listing   Taiwan   separated   from   China   hostility   is   not   good   to   the   peace
and   stability   of   the   large   part   of   people   and   area   in   the   world .
　
Google ,   as   a   venerable   hi - tech   company ,   what   can   change   your   represent   hasti
ly   without   justness ?   Democracy ?   Minoral   unreasonable   remonstrate ?   I   am   sure
we   will   have   a   much   larger   number   of   mail   to   show   the   right   way .
　
Pease   readd   “ Province   of   China ”   on   the   statement   of   Taiwan .   And ,   do   not   di
splay   Taiwan   ( Hongkong ,   Macro )   with   China   together   in   the   same   screen   resolu
tion   ( such   as   1000km   scale ) .   Like   the   Hawaii   and   United   States   on   your   websi
te .
　
Thanks .
　
